'''番茄牛肉通心粉'''（簡稱'''茄牛通'''）是[[香港|香港]]的一種[[通心粉|通心粉]]餐點<ref name="hk01-2017-11-29">{{cite news |title=番茄通粉湯底健康清新　牛肉如何做到嫩滑不韌？ |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F/137249/%E8%8C%84%E7%89%9B%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C-%E7%95%AA%E8%8C%84%E9%80%9A%E7%B2%89%E6%B9%AF%E5%BA%95%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%B8%85%E6%96%B0-%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%81%9A%E5%88%B0%E5%AB%A9%E6%BB%91%E4%B8%8D%E9%9F%8C |accessdate=2019-06-16 |work=香港01 |date=2017-11-29 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616114719/https://www.hk01.com/%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F/137249/%E8%8C%84%E7%89%9B%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C-%E7%95%AA%E8%8C%84%E9%80%9A%E7%B2%89%E6%B9%AF%E5%BA%95%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%B8%85%E6%96%B0-%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%81%9A%E5%88%B0%E5%AB%A9%E6%BB%91%E4%B8%8D%E9%9F%8C |dead-url=no }}</ref>，源於香港的[[大牌檔|大牌檔]]<ref name="蕃茄牛肉麵達人">{{cite news |title=勝香園 蕃茄牛肉麵達人 |url=http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/archive/taodongfood/27659 |accessdate=2021-06-01 |work=香港經濟日報 |date=2014-09-24 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616114933/https://www.gotrip.hk/378405/foods/%e8%a8%98%e8%80%85%e8%a9%a6%e9%a3%9f-top-7-%e7%95%aa%e8%8c%84%e7%89%9b%e8%82%89%e9%80%9a%e7%b2%89/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，特色是將來自西方的[[通心粉|通心粉]]與東方的湯麵烹調手法融為一體<ref name="意大利人試食港式意粉">{{cite news |title=居港10年意大利人試食港式意粉 見到叉燒湯意粉嚇親 「係我嘅敵人！」 |url=https://hk.appledaily.com/ETW/20200728/W54GENG4IXXTFMAMO542QSIZD4/ |accessdate=2021-06-01 |work=蘋果日報 |date=2021-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605105019/https://hk.appledaily.com/ETW/20200728/W54GENG4IXXTFMAMO542QSIZD4/ |archive-date=2021-06-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，成為匯聚東西文化的港式麵食<ref name="為何出現湯意粉">{{cite news |title=茶餐廳為何出現湯意粉？茶記9大受外國影響美食 |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E9%A3%9F%E7%8E%A9%E8%B2%B7/565534/%E8%8C%B6%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E6%B9%AF%E6%84%8F%E7%B2%89-%E8%8C%B6%E8%A8%989%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F-%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E5%91%B3-12 |accessdate=2021-06-01 |work=香港01 |date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603153547/https://www.hk01.com/%E9%A3%9F%E7%8E%A9%E8%B2%B7/565534/%E8%8C%B6%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E6%B9%AF%E6%84%8F%E7%B2%89-%E8%8C%B6%E8%A8%989%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F-%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E5%91%B3-12 |archive-date=2021-06-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。茄牛通以[[番茄|番茄]]及[[牛肉|牛肉]]煮成的肉湯，並配上[[意大利粉|意大利粉]]之一的通心粉，味道酸中帶甜很開胃<ref name="udn-2018-01-31">{{cite news |title=香港好厲害的路邊攤 奶油脆脆＆番茄通粉必點！ |url=https://udn.com/news/story/7173/2950539 |accessdate=2019-06-16 |work=聯合新聞網 |date=2018-01-31 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616115245/https://udn.com/news/story/7173/2950539 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。現在常見於香港的[[茶餐廳|茶餐廳]]<ref name="GOtrip-2017">{{cite news |title=記者試食 Top 7 番茄牛肉通粉！華嫂冰室茄牛通湯底足料 中環勝香園啖啖茄肉 |url=https://www.gotrip.hk/378405/foods/%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A9%A6%E9%A3%9F-top-7-%E7%95%AA%E8%8C%84%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E9%80%9A%E7%B2%89/ |accessdate=2019-06-16 |work=GOtrip |date=2017-11-02 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616114933/https://www.gotrip.hk/378405/foods/%e8%a8%98%e8%80%85%e8%a9%a6%e9%a3%9f-top-7-%e7%95%aa%e8%8c%84%e7%89%9b%e8%82%89%e9%80%9a%e7%b2%89/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，香港的[[港式快餐|港式快餐]]在早市和下午茶時段亦有提供此菜式。

